## Choosing a Provider

### 🆓 Free Providers (Recommended to Start)

#### OpenRouter
- **Best For:** Access to 200+ models through one API
- **Free Models:** Llama 3.3 70B, Gemini 2.0 Flash, Mistral
- **Get API Key:** [openrouter.ai/keys](https://openrouter.ai/keys)
- **Why Choose:** Most flexible option, many free models

#### Groq
- **Best For:** Lightning-fast responses
- **Free Models:** Llama 3.3, Mixtral, Gemma 2
- **Get API Key:** [console.groq.com/keys](https://console.groq.com/keys)
- **Why Choose:** Fastest inference (custom LPU hardware)

#### HuggingFace
- **Best For:** Thousands of open-source models
- **Free Models:** Many options
- **Get API Key:** [huggingface.co/settings/tokens](https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens)
- **Why Choose:** True free tier, no credit card needed

#### Mistral
- **Best For:** European AI (GDPR-friendly)
- **Free Models:** Limited free usage
- **Get API Key:** [console.mistral.ai/api-keys/](https://console.mistral.ai/api-keys/)
- **Why Choose:** Privacy-focused, European option

### 💳 Paid Providers (Bring Your Own Key)

#### Google Gemini
- **Best For:** Large context (1M tokens!)
- **Models:** Flash (fast), Pro (advanced)
- **Get API Key:** [aistudio.google.com/apikey](https://aistudio.google.com/apikey)
- **Cost:** Pay-per-use

#### OpenAI
- **Best For:** GPT-4o, o1 reasoning models
- **Models:** GPT-4o, GPT-4o Mini, o1, o1-mini
- **Get API Key:** [platform.openai.com/api-keys](https://platform.openai.com/api-keys)
- **Cost:** $0.15-$15 per 1M tokens
- **Note:** Requires backend proxy (CORS limitation)

#### Anthropic Claude
- **Best For:** Thoughtful analysis, writing
- **Models:** Claude 3.5 Sonnet, Haiku, Opus
- **Get API Key:** [console.anthropic.com/settings/keys](https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys)
- **Cost:** $1-$15 per 1M tokens
- **Special:** Works in browser! (CORS supported)

#### xAI Grok
- **Best For:** Unique personality, real-time info
- **Models:** Grok Beta, Grok Vision
- **Get API Key:** [console.x.ai](https://console.x.ai)
- **Cost:** Estimated $5 per 1M tokens
- **Note:** Requires backend proxy (CORS limitation)

